### ================================================
### 모니터링 & 상태 확인
### ================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### ================================================
### 1. Health Check
### ================================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/health
Content-Type: application/json

### ================================================
### 2. Circuit Breaker 상태 조회
### (management.endpoints.web.exposure.include에 circuitbreakers 추가 필요)
### ================================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/circuitbreakers
Content-Type: application/json

### ================================================
### 3. Circuit Breaker 이벤트 조회
### ================================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/circuitbreakerevents
Content-Type: application/json

### ================================================
### 4. Prometheus 메트릭
### ================================================
GET {{baseUrl}}/actuator/prometheus
Content-Type: application/json

